#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:985
#, no-c-format
msgid "HlCStringChar"
msgstr "HICStringChar"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detect an escaped character."
msgstr "Tuvastab paomärgi."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:988
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;HlCStringChar (common attributes) /&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;HlCStringChar (üldatribuudid) /&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It matches literal representations of characters commonly used in program "
"code, for example <userinput>\\n</userinput> (newline) or <userinput>\\t</"
"userinput> (TAB)."
msgstr ""
"See otsib sobivusi nähtamatutele märkidele, mida tihti programmikoodis "
"kasutatakse, näiteks <userinput>\\n</userinput> (uus rida) või <userinput>"
"\\t</userinput> (tabeldusmärk)."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following characters will match if they follow a backslash (<literal>\\</"
"literal>): <userinput>abefnrtv&quot;'?\\</userinput>. Additionally, escaped "
"hexadecimal numbers such as for example <userinput>\\xff</userinput> and "
"escaped octal numbers, for example <userinput>\\033</userinput> will match."
msgstr ""
"Leitakse järgmised märgid, kui neile eelneb längkriips (<literal>\\</"
"literal>): <userinput>abefnrtv&quot;'?\\</userinput>. Lisaks leitakse "
"kuueteistkümnendsüsteemis varjestatud arvud, näiteks <userinput>\\xff</"
"userinput>, ja kaheksandsüsteemis varjestatud arvud, näiteks <userinput>"
"\\033</userinput>."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid "HlCChar"
msgstr "HlCChar"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1008
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detect an C character."
msgstr "Tuvastab C märgi."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:1009
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;HlCChar (common attributes) /&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;HlCChar (üldatribuudid) /&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It matches C characters enclosed in a tick (Example: <userinput>'c'</"
"userinput>). The ticks may be a simple character or an escaped character. "
"See HlCStringChar for matched escaped character sequences."
msgstr ""
"Leitakse ülakriipsude vahele võetud C märgid, näiteks <userinput>'c'</"
"userinput>. Ülakriipsude vahel võib olla lihtne märk või ka varjestatud "
"märk. Viimaste kohta vaata HlCStringChar."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid "RangeDetect"
msgstr "RangeDetect"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detect a string with defined start and end characters."
msgstr "Tuvastab stringi määratud algus- ja lõpumärgiga."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;RangeDetect char=&quot;(character)&quot;  char1=&quot;(character)&quot; "
"(common attributes) /&gt;"
msgstr ""
"&lt;RangeDetect char=&quot;(märk)&quot;  char1=&quot;(märk)&quot; "
"(üldatribuudid) /&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1024
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>char</userinput> defines the character starting the range, "
"<userinput>char1</userinput> the character ending the range."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>char</userinput> määrab vahemikku alustava märgi ning "
"<userinput>char1</userinput> seda lõpetava märgi."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Useful to detect for example small quoted strings and the like, but note "
"that since the highlighting engine works on one line at a time, this will "
"not find strings spanning over a line break."
msgstr ""
"See on kasulik näiteks väiksemate jutumärkides stringides ja muu sellise "
"leidmiseks, kuid tasub tähele panna, et esiletõstu mootor töötab korraga "
"ühel real ega leia stringe, mis ulatuvad üle reapiiri."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid "LineContinue"
msgstr "LineContinue"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1035
#, no-c-format
msgid "Matches a specified char at the end of a line."
msgstr "Tuvastab määratud märgi rea lõpus."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;LineContinue (common attributes) [char=\"\\\"] /&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;LineContinue (üldatribuudid) [char=\"\\\"] /&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1037
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<userinput>char</userinput> optional character to match, default is "
#| "backslash (<userinput>'\\'</userinput>). New since KDE 4.13."
msgid ""
"<userinput>char</userinput> optional character to match, default is "
"backslash (<userinput>'\\'</userinput>). New since &kde; 4.13."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>char</userinput> on täiendav tuvastatav märk, vaikimisi "
"längkriips (<userinput>'\\'</userinput>. Uus asi alates &kde;  4.13."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This rule is useful for switching context at end of line. This is needed for "
"example in C/C++ to continue macros or strings."
msgstr ""
"See reegel on abiks konteksti lülitamisel rea lõpus. Seda vajab näiteks C/C+"
"+ makrode või stringide jätkamiseks."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1045
#, no-c-format
msgid "IncludeRules"
msgstr "IncludeRules"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1047
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include rules from another context or language/file."
msgstr "Kaasatakse teise konteksti või keele/faili reeglid."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;IncludeRules context=&quot;contextlink&quot; [includeAttrib=&quot;true|"
"false&quot;] /&gt;"
msgstr ""
"&lt;IncludeRules context=&quot;kontekstilink&quot; [includeAttrib=&quot;true|"
"false&quot;] /&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <userinput>context</userinput> attribute defines which context to "
"include."
msgstr ""
"Atribuut <userinput>context</userinput> määrab, milline kontekst kaasata."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If it is a simple string it includes all defined rules into the current "
"context, example:"
msgstr ""
"Kui see on lihtne string, kaasatakse aktiivsesse konteksti kõik defineeritud "
"reeglid, näiteks:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;IncludeRules context=&quot;anotherContext&quot; /&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;IncludeRules context=&quot;teineKontekst&quot; /&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the string contains a <userinput>##</userinput> the highlight system will "
"look for a context from another language definition with the given name, for "
"example <programlisting>&lt;IncludeRules context=&quot;String##C++&quot; /"
"&gt;</programlisting> would include the context <emphasis>String</emphasis> "
"from the <emphasis>C++</emphasis> highlighting definition."
msgstr ""
"Kui string sisaldab <userinput>##</userinput>, otsib esiletõstmise süsteem "
"konteksti teise, antud nimega keele definitsioonist, näiteks "
"<programlisting>&lt;IncludeRules context=&quot;String##C++&quot; /&gt;</"
"programlisting> kaasab konteksti <emphasis>String</emphasis> <emphasis>C++</"
"emphasis> esiletõstmise definitsioonist."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1061
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <userinput>includeAttrib</userinput> attribute is <emphasis>true</"
"emphasis>, change the destination attribute to the one of the source. This "
"is required to make, for example, commenting work, if text matched by the "
"included context is a different highlight from the host context."
msgstr ""
"Kui atribuut <userinput>includeAttrib</userinput> on tõene (<emphasis>true</"
"emphasis>), muudetakse sihtatribuut lähteatribuudiks. Seda on vaja näiteks "
"kommenteerimise jaoks, kui kaasatud kontekstis sobiv tekst on teistsuguse "
"esiletõstuga kui algkontekstis."

#. Tag: term
#: development.docbook:1072
#, no-c-format
msgid "DetectSpaces"
msgstr "DetectSpaces"

#. Tag: para
