#| "Z0-9_]*)."
msgid ""
"Detect identifier strings (as the regular expression: <userinput>[a-zA-Z_][a-"
"zA-Z0-9_]*</userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Tuvastab identifikaatoristringid (regulaaravaldisena [a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_]*)."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
