"Highlighting repository</ulink>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you repeat complex regular expression very often you can use "
"<emphasis>ENTITIES</emphasis>. Example:"
msgstr ""
"Sageli keerukaid regulaaravaldisi vajades võiks kasutada olemeid "
"(<emphasis>ENTITIES</emphasis>). Näide:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: development.docbook:1167
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
