msgid ""
"Truncate the given line at the given column or cursor position. Returns "
"<literal>true</literal> on success, or <literal>false</literal> if the given "
"line is not part of the document range."
msgstr ""
"Kärbib määratud rea määratud veeruga või kursori asukohaga. Tagastab "
"<literal>true</literal> õnnestumise korral või <literal>false</literal>, kui "
"määratud rida ei kuulu dokumendi vahemikku."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>veerg</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>String <replaceable>tekst</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.insertText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>kursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>tekst</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts the <replaceable>text</replaceable> at the given cursor position. "
"Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, or <literal>false</literal>, if "
"the document is in read-only mode."
msgstr ""
"Lisab <replaceable>teksti</replaceable> määratud kursori asukohta. Tagastab "
"<literal>true</literal> õnnestumise korral või <literal>false</literal>, kui "
"dokument on kirjutuskaitstud."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>int <replaceable>fromLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>fromColumn</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>toLine</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>toColumn</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>from</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>Cursor <replaceable>to</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Range <replaceable>range</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>int <replaceable>alatesReast</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>alatesVeerust</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>kuniReani</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>kuniVeeruni</"
"replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>alates</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>Cursor <replaceable>kuni</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"bool document.removeText(<parameter>Range <replaceable>vahemik</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the text in the given range. Returns <literal>true</literal> on "
"success, or <literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode."
msgstr ""
"Eemaldab teksti määratud vahemikus. Tagastab <literal>true</literal> "
"õnnestumise korral või <literal>false</literal>, kui dokument on "
"kirjutuskaitstud."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.insertLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>text</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.insertLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>String <replaceable>tekst</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts text in the given line. Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, "
"or <literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode or the "
"line is not in the document range."
msgstr ""
"Lisab teksti määratud reale. Tagastab <literal>true</literal> õnnestumise "
"korral või <literal>false</literal>, kui dokument on kirjutuskaitstud või "
"rida ei paikne dokumendi vahemikus."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.removeLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.removeLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the given text line. Returns <literal>true</literal> on success, or "
"<literal>false</literal>, if the document is in read-only mode or the line "
"is not in the document range."
msgstr ""
"Eemaldab määratud tekstirea. Tagastab <literal>true</literal> õnnestumise "
"korral või <literal>false</literal>, kui dokument on kirjutuskaitstud või "
"rida ei paikne dokumendi vahemikus."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>veerg</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.wrapLine(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>kursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wraps the line at the given cursor position. Returns <literal>true</literal> "
"on success, otherwise <literal>false</literal>, &eg; if line &lt; 0."
msgstr ""
"Murrab rida määratud kursori asukohas. Tagastab <literal>true</literal> "
"õnnestumise korral või <literal>false</literal>, kui nt. rida &lt; 0."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3506
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"void document.joinLines(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>endLine</replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"void document.joinLines(<parameter>int <replaceable>algusRida</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>lõppRida</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Joins the lines from <replaceable>startLine</replaceable> to "
"<replaceable>endLine</replaceable>. Two succeeding text lines are always "
"separated with a single space."
msgstr ""
"Ühendab read alates <replaceable>algusRida</replaceable> to "
"<replaceable>lõppRida</replaceable>. Kaht järjestikust tekstirida eraldab "
"alati üks tühik."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3515
#, no-c-format
msgid "int document.lines();"
msgstr "int document.lines();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the number of lines in the document."
msgstr "Tagastab dokumendi ridade arvu."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineModified(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineModified(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"currently contains unsaved data."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab <literal>true</literal>, kui <replaceable>rida</replaceable> "
"sisaldab parajasti salvestamata andmeid."

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3527 development.docbook:3539 development.docbook:3550
#: development.docbook:3562 development.docbook:3736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kde; 5.0"
msgstr "Alates: &kde; 5.0"

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineSaved(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineSaved(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> was "
"changed, but the document was saved. Hence, the line currently does not "
"contain any unsaved data."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab <literal>true</literal>, kui <replaceable>rida</replaceable> on "
"muudetud, aga dokument on salvestatud, nii et real ei leidu parajasti "
"salvestamata andmeid."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isLineTouched(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isLineTouched(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if <replaceable>line</replaceable> "
"currently contains unsaved data or was changed before."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab <literal>true</literal>, kui <replaceable>rida</replaceable> "
"sisaldab parajasti salvestamata andmeid või seda on varem muudetud."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.findTouchedLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>startLine</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>bool <replaceable>down</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.findTouchedLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>algusRida</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>bool <replaceable>alla</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search for the next touched line starting at <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. The search is performed either upwards or downwards depending "
"on the search direction specified in <replaceable>down</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Otsib järgmist muudetud rida alates määratud <replaceable>reast</"
"replaceable>. Otsing võetakse ette kas üles- või allapoole sõltuvalt "
"otsingusuunast, mille määrab kindlaks <replaceable>alla</replaceable>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3569
#, no-c-format
msgid "int document.length();"
msgstr "int document.length();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the number of characters in the document."
msgstr "Tagastab dokumendi sümbolite arvu."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lineLength(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lineLength(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the <replaceable>line</replaceable>'s length."
msgstr "Tagastab <replaceable>rea</replaceable> pikkuse."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3585
#, no-c-format
msgid "void document.editBegin();"
msgstr "void document.editBegin();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts an edit group for undo/redo grouping. Make sure to always call "
"<function>editEnd()</function> as often as you call <function>editBegin()</"
"function>. Calling <function>editBegin()</function> internally uses a "
"reference counter, &ie;, this call can be nested."
msgstr ""
"Alustab redigeerimisrühma tagasivõtmiste või uuestitegemiste rühmitamiseks. "
"Kontrolli, et <function>editEnd()</function> oleks alati sama palju välja "
"kutsutud kui <function>editBegin()</function>. <function>editBegin()</"
"function> väljakutse kasutab seesmiselt referentsarvestit, s.t selle "
"väljakutse korral on võimalik pesastamine."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3596
#, no-c-format
msgid "void document.editEnd();"
msgstr "void document.editEnd();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ends an edit group. The last call of <function>editEnd()</function> (&ie; "
"the one for the first call of <function>editBegin()</function>) finishes the "
"edit step."
msgstr ""
"Lõpetab redigeerimisrühma. Viimane <function>editEnd()</function> väljakutse "
"(s.t see, mis vastab esimesele <function>editBegin()</function> "
"väljakutsele) lõpetab redigeerimisastme."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.firstColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.firstColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the first non-whitespace column in the given <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. If there are only whitespaces in the line, the return value is "
"<literal>-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab määratud <replaceable>rea</replaceable> esimese mittetühimärgiga "
"veeru. Kui real on ainult tühimärgid, tagastatakse <literal>-1</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3615
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.lastColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.lastColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the last non-whitespace column in the given <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable>. If there are only whitespaces in the line, the return value is "
"<literal>-1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab määratud <replaceable>rea</replaceable> viimase mittetühimärgiga "
"veeru. Kui real on ainult tühimärgid, tagastatakse <literal>-1</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>veerg</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.prevNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>kursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the column with a non-whitespace character starting at the given "
"cursor position and searching backwards."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab mittetühimärkidega veeru alates aktiivsest kursori asukohast "
"tagasisuunas otsides."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>veerg</replaceable></"
"parameter>);\n"
"int document.nextNonSpaceColumn(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>kursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the column with a non-whitespace character starting at the given "
"cursor position and searching forwards."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab mittetühimärkidega veeru alates aktiivsest kursori asukohast "
"edasisuunas otsides."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.prevNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.prevNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the next non-empty line containing non-whitespace characters "
"searching backwards."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab järgmise mittetühimärkidega mittetühja rea, otsides tagasisuunas."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.nextNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.nextNonEmptyLine(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the next non-empty line containing non-whitespace characters "
"searching forwards."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab järgmise mittetühimärkidega mittetühja rea, otsides edasisuunas."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isInWord(<parameter>String <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isInWord(<parameter>String <replaceable>sümbol</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>atribuut</replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable> with the given <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> can be part "
"of a word, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab <literal>true</literal>, kui määratud <replaceable>sümbol</"
"replaceable> määratud <replaceable>atribuudiga</replaceable> võib olla sõna "
"osa, vastasel juhul <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.canBreakAt(<parameter>String <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.canBreakAt(<parameter>String <replaceable>sümbol</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>atribuut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given <replaceable>character</"
"replaceable> with the given <replaceable>attribute</replaceable> is suited "
"to wrap a line, otherwise <literal>false</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab <literal>true</literal>, kui määratud <replaceable>sümbol</"
"replaceable> määratud <replaceable>atribuudiga</replaceable> sobib "
"reamurdmiseks, vastasel juhul <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.canComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>startAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>endAttribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.canComment(<parameter>int <replaceable>algusAtribuut</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>lõppAtribuut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if a range starting and ending with the "
"given attributes is suited to be commented out, otherwise <literal>false</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab <literal>true</literal>, kui määratud atribuudiga algav ja lõppev "
"vahemik sobib kommenteerimiseks, vastasel juhul <literal>false</literal>."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentMarker(<parameter>int <replaceable>atribuut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for single line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab kommentaaritähise määratud <replaceable>atribuudiga</replaceable> "
"üherealise kommentaari puhul."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentStart(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentStart(<parameter>int <replaceable>atribuut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for the start of multi-line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab kommentaaritähise määratud <replaceable>atribuudiga</replaceable> "
"mitmerealise kommentaari alguse puhul."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"String document.commentEnd(<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"String document.commentEnd(<parameter>int <replaceable>atribuut</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the comment marker for the end of multi-line comments for a given "
"<replaceable>attribute</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab kommentaaritähise määratud <replaceable>atribuudiga</replaceable> "
"mitmerealise kommentaari lõpu puhul."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Range document.documentRange();"
msgstr "Range document.documentRange();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3716
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns a range that encompasses the whole document."
msgstr "Tagastab kogu dokumenti hõlmava vahemiku."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3723
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor documentEnd();"
msgstr "Cursor documentEnd();"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns a cursor positioned at the last column of the last line in the "
"document."
msgstr "Tagastab kursori dokumendi viimase rea viimases veerus."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>veerg</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool isValidTextPosition(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>kursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns <literal>true</literal>, if the given cursor position is positioned "
"at a valid text position. A text position is valid only if it locate at the "
"start, in the middle, or the end of a valid line. Further, a text position "
"is invalid if it is located in a Unicode surrogate."
msgstr ""
"Tagastab <literal>true</literal>, kui määratud kursor asub sobivas "
"tekstikohas. Tekstikoht on sobiv ainult siis, kui see asub sobiva rea "
"alguses, keskel või lõpus. Lisaks ei ole tekstikoht sobiv, kui see asub "
"Unicode'i surrogaadis."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"int document.attribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.attribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"int document.attribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>veerg</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"int document.attribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>kursor</replaceable></"
"parameter>);"

#. Tag: para
#: development.docbook:3744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the attribute at the given cursor position."
msgstr "Tagastab atribuudi määratud kursori asukohas."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: development.docbook:3751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>line</replaceable></"
"parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>column</replaceable></parameter>, "
"<parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</replaceable></parameter>);\n"
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>Cursor <replaceable>cursor</"
"replaceable></parameter>, <parameter>int <replaceable>attribute</"
"replaceable></parameter>);"
msgstr ""
"bool document.isAttribute(<parameter>int <replaceable>rida</replaceable></"
